00:02:12.990 --> 00:02:14.300
Yeah, it does.

00:02:14.300 --> 00:02:16.660
And a 2010 study from Plos ONE explains why…

00:02:16.660 --> 00:02:20.080
See, the foreskin isn't just an extra bit
on the bits.

00:02:20.080 --> 00:02:27.030
Because the foreskin is a protective, mucous-membrane
